Sharapova Beats Petkovic to Play Li Na in French Open Tennis Semifinals

-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 
2011-06-01T13:43:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-01/sharapova-beats-petkovic-to-play-li-na-in-french-open-tennis-semifinals.html
Maria Sharapova  defeated  Andrea
Petkovic  of Germany 6-0, 6-3 to advance to the semifinals of the
French Open tennis championship in Paris.  Sharapova, the seventh seed from  Russia , is seeking to
complete the career Grand Slam with her first French Open title.
She’ll face No. 6 Li Na of  China , who beat fourth-seeded
 Victoria Azarenka  of Belarus 7-5, 6-2 in today’s other
quarterfinal.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  